<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to {{appName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .welcome-message {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #28a745;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .features {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .feature-item {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .feature-item:before {
            content: "âœ“";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .social-links a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">{{appName}}</div>
            <div class="welcome-message">Welcome Aboard, {{userName}}! ðŸŽ‰</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Thank you for joining <strong>{{appName}}</strong>! We're excited to have you as part of our trading community.</p>
            
            <p>Your account has been successfully created and linked to your Telegram account <strong>@{{telegramUsername}}</strong>.</p>
            
            <div class="features">
                <h3>What you can do now:</h3>
                <div class="feature-item">Browse our subscription plans to access premium trading alerts</div>
                <div class="feature-item">Configure your trading preferences and risk settings</div>
                <div class="feature-item">Connect with our Telegram bot for real-time notifications</div>
                <div class="feature-item">Access detailed analytics and trade history</div>
                <div class="feature-item">Join our community of successful traders</div>
            </div>
            
            <p>To get started, we recommend:</p>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Choose a subscription plan</strong> that fits your trading style</li>
                <li><strong>Set up your preferences</strong> for alerts and notifications</li>
                <li><strong>Start receiving</strong> high-quality trading signals</li>
            </ol>
            
            <p>Our team is here to help you succeed. If you have any questions, don't hesitate to reach out!</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">Telegram Channel</a> |
                <a href="#">Support</a> |
                <a href="#">FAQ</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p><small>You received this email because you signed up for {{appName}}.</small></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>